No, not signing that striker from Ebbsfleet Town on a loan deal that was a hit for you on Football Manager. Kit unveiling day.
Football fans are renowned for many things, but becoming fashion experts when their favourite team brings out their latest offering is a yearly ritual these days.
So who wears it well this season? Have a look at these home kits and get ranking. And, remember, be honest...
